trans-unit.source: Exposes a generic <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of designer glyphs associated with an activity designer.
trans-unit.target: Expõe um genérico <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> do estruturador glyphs associados um designer de atividade.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection contains all designer glyphs that appear on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> class with which the collection is associated.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection contém todos os glifos estruturador que aparecem no <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>classe a que a coleção está associada.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: You can access the contents of the ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection through the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Pode aceder ao conteúdo de ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection através de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"></xref> class that is empty and has the default initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"> </xref> classe que está vazio e tem a capacidade inicial predefinido.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"></xref> class that contains elements copied from the specified generic collection of <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph"></xref>, and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"> </xref> classe que contém elementos copiada a partir da coleção de genérica especificada <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph"> </xref>, e tem capacidade suficiente para acomodar o número de elementos copiados.
Que contém a coleção genérica enumeráveis <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"></xref> class that contains elements copied from the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"></xref> and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"> </xref> classe que contém elementos copiados especificado <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"> </xref> e tem capacidade suficiente para acomodar o número de elementos copiados.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"></xref> from which to copy collection elements.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection"> </xref> partir dos quais pretende copiar os elementos da coleção.
